        <h1>Cho ben thanh</h1>
                <img src="https://www.citypassguide.com/media/slideshow/SG-BenThanhNight-04.06-WI10-L.01.jpg.1024x768_q85.jpg">
        <p>One can not fail to mention this place first when it has been considered a symbol of Saigon for decades. This market is located in the central district 1 of the city, next to Quach Thi Trang Square and 23/9 park. Location is the reason why this market is bustling, crowded. Ben Thanh Market was started construction, completed in the early years of the 20th century and has been operating continuously since then.</p>
        <p>With more than 3,000 stalls in the market, there are a wide variety of wholesale and retail goods, from affordable to luxury, so you can say that the products here are extremely diverse. From 8-9 am is the time when the stalls and counters open all the time, so from this time on, the market is always busy with the sellers, the space is really bustling..</p>
